  17. (* Reloading for the ARM 64 bits *)

  19. open Reg

  21. class reload = object (self)

  23. inherit Reloadgen.reload_generic as super

  25. method! reload_operation op arg res =
  26.   match op with
  27.   | Ispecific Imove32 ->
  28.       (* Like Imove: argument or result can be on stack but not both *)
  29.       begin match arg.(0), res.(0) with
  30.       | {loc = Stack s1}, {loc = Stack s2} when s1 <> s2 ->
  31.           ([| self#makereg arg.(0) |], res)
  32.       | _ ->
  33.           (arg, res)
  34.       end
  35.    | _ ->
  36.       super#reload_operation op arg res

  38. end

  41.   (new reload)#fundecl f num_stack_slots
